<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>StudyFlow - Réseau Médical Étudiant</title>
    <!-- Font Awesome 6 (gratuit) -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <!-- Google Fonts -->
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #1e293b;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f1f5f9 0%, #e6edf5 100%);
            padding: 40px 20px;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.95);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border-radius: 32px;
            box-shadow: 0 25px 50px -12px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
            padding: 40px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
        }
        
        /* Header Premium */
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(145deg, #0f2b4b, #1a3a5c);
            color: white;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 35px;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 30px -10px rgba(15,43,75,0.3);
        }
        
        .header::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: -50%;
            right: -50%;
            width: 200%;
            height: 200%;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,255,255,0.1) 0%, transparent 70%);
            animation: pulse 8s ease infinite;
        }
        
        @keyframes pulse {
            0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 0.5; }
            50% { transform: scale(1.1); opacity: 0.8; }
        }
        
        .header-content {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }
        
        .brand {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 15px;
        }
        
        .brand-icon {
            font-size: 48px;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 18px;
            backdrop-filter: blur(5px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
        }
        
        .brand-text h1 {
            font-size: 36px;
            font-weight: 800;
            letter-spacing: -1px;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff, #e0e7ff);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }
        
        .brand-text p {
            font-size: 15px;
            opacity: 0.9;
            font-weight: 400;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
        }
        
        .date-badge {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            backdrop-filter: blur(5px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
            font-weight: 500;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }
        
        .date-badge i {
            color: #93c5fd;
        }
        
        /* Alerte Urgence */
        .emergency-alert {
            background: linear-gradient(145deg, #7f1d1d, #991b1b);
            color: white;
            padding: 20px 30px;
            border-radius: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px -8px rgba(153,27,27,0.3);
        }
        
        .emergency-left {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 20px;
        }
        
        .emergency-icon {
            font-size: 32px;
            animation: pulse-emergency 1.5s ease infinite;
        }
        
        @keyframes pulse-emergency {
            0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 1; }
            50% { transform: scale(1.1); opacity: 0.8; }
        }
        
        .emergency-numbers {
            display: flex;
            gap: 25px;
        }
        
        .emergency-number {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            font-weight: 700;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            backdrop-filter: blur(5px);
        }
        
        /* Sections */
        .section {
            margin-bottom: 45px;
        }
        
        .section-header {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }
        
        .section-title {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
        }
        
        .section-icon {
            font-size: 28px;
            color: #0f2b4b;
            background: linear-gradient(145deg, #e6f0ff, #ffffff);
            padding: 12px;
            border-radius: 16px;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px -5px rgba(15,43,75,0.1);
        }
        
        .section-title h2 {
            font-size: 26px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #0f2b4b;
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
        }
        
        .section-badge {
            background: #e6f0ff;
            color: #0f2b4b;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 600;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
        }
        
        /* Table Design */
        .table-container {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 20px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 20px -8px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
            border: 1px solid #eef2f6;
        }
        
        table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
        }
        
        thead {
            background: linear-gradient(145deg, #f8fafc, #f1f5f9);
            border-bottom: 2px solid #e2e8f0;
        }
        
        th {
            padding: 18px 20px;
            text-align: left;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #1e293b;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }
        
        td {
            padding: 18px 20px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #eef2f6;
            font-size: 15px;
            color: #334155;
        }
        
        tbody tr {
            transition: all 0.2s ease;
        }
        
        tbody tr:hover {
            background: linear-gradient(145deg, #f1f9ff, #f8fafc);
            transform: scale(1.01);
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px -8px rgba(15,43,75,0.1);
        }
        
        tbody tr:last-child td {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        
        /* Badges */
        .badge {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 6px;
            padding: 8px 14px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: 0.3px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
        }
        
        .badge-primary {
            background: linear-gradient(145deg, #e6f0ff, #d4e6ff);
            color: #0f2b4b;
            border: 1px solid rgba(15,43,75,0.1);
        }
        
        .badge-success {
            background: linear-gradient(145deg, #e6f7e6, #d4f0d4);
            color: #0a4a2e;
            border: 1px solid rgba(10,74,46,0.1);
        }
        
        .badge-info {
            background: linear-gradient(145deg, #e6f3fa, #d4ebf5);
            color: #0369a1;
            border: 1px solid rgba(3,105,161,0.1);
        }
        
        .phone {
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #0f2b4b;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
        }
        
        .phone i {
            color: #3b82f6;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        
        .address {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            color: #64748b;
        }
        
        .address i {
            color: #94a3b8;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        
        /* Footer */
        .footer {
            margin-top: 50px;
            background: linear-gradient(145deg, #f8fafc, #f1f5f9);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 35px;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr;
            gap: 30px;
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }
        
        .footer-info h3 {
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #0f2b4b;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }
        
        .footer-info p {
            color: #475569;
            font-size: 15px;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }
        
        .footer-stats {
            display: flex;
            gap: 20px;
            justify-content: flex-end;
        }
        
        .stat-item {
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .stat-value {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: #0f2b4b;
        }
        
        .stat-label {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #64748b;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }
        
        .confidential {
            margin-top: 25px;
            padding-top: 25px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            text-align: center;
            color: #64748b;
            font-size: 13px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }
        
        /* Responsive */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .container {
                padding: 20px;
            }
            
            .header-content {
                flex-direction: column;
                text-align: center;
                gap: 20px;
            }
            
            .emergency-alert {
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 15px;
            }
            
            .emergency-numbers {
                flex-wrap: wrap;
                justify-content: center;
            }
            
            .footer {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
            
            .footer-stats {
                justify-content: flex-start;
            }
        }
        
        @media print {
            body {
                background: white;
                padding: 0;
            }
            
            .container {
                box-shadow: none;
                padding: 20px;
            }
            
            .emergency-alert {
                break-inside: avoid;
            }
            
            .table-container {
                break-inside: auto;
            }
            
            tr {
                break-inside: avoid;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <!-- Header Premium -->
        <div class="header">
            <div class="header-content">
                <div class="brand">
                    <div class="brand-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-brain"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="brand-text">
                        <h1>StudyFlow</h1>
                        <p>
                            <i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i>
                            Santé & Bien-être étudiant
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="date-badge">
                    <i class="fas fa-calendar-alt"></i>
                    {{ date|date('d.m.Y') }}
                    <i class="fas fa-clock" style="margin-left: 10px;"></i>
                    {{ date|date('H:i') }}
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Alerte Urgence Premium -->
        <div class="emergency-alert">
            <div class="emergency-left">
                <div class="emergency-icon">
                    <i class="fas fa-circle-exclamation"></i>
                </div>
                <div style="font-weight: 600; font-size: 18px;">
                    Urgences médicales 24h/24
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="emergency-numbers">
                <div class="emergency-number">
                    <i class="fas fa-ambulance"></i>
                    <span>SAMU: 190</span>
                </div>
                <div class="emergency-number">
                    <i class="fas fa-shield"></i>
                    <span>Protection Civile: 198</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Section Psychiatres -->
        <div class="section">
            <div class="section-header">
                <div class="section-title">
                    <div class="section-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-user-md"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h2>Psychiatres & Psychologues</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="section-badge">
                    <i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i>
                    {{ medicalData.psychiatrists|length }} praticiens
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="table-container">
                <table>
                    <thead>
                        <tr>
                            <th>Praticien</th>
                            <th>Spécialité</th>
                            <th>Contact</th>
                            <th>Localisation</th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                        {% for doctor in medicalData.psychiatrists %}
                        <tr>
                            <td>
                                <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;">
                                    <i class="fas fa-user-circle" style="color: #0f2b4b; font-size: 20px;"></i>
                                    <strong style="font-size: 16px;">{{ doctor.name }}</strong>
                                </div>
                            </td>
                            <td>
                                <span class="badge badge-primary">
                                    <i class="fas fa-stethoscope"></i>
                                    {{ doctor.specialty }}
                                </span>
                            </td>
                            <td>
                                <span class="phone">
                                    <i class="fas fa-phone-alt"></i>
                                    {{ doctor.phone }}
                                </span>
                            </td>
                            <td>
                                <span class="address">
                                    <i class="fas fa-location-dot"></i>
                                    {{ doctor.address }}
                                </span>
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                        {% endfor %}
                    </tbody>
                </table>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Section Pharmacies -->
        <div class="section">
            <div class="section-header">
                <div class="section-title">
                    <div class="section-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-prescription-bottle"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h2>Pharmacies de garde</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="section-badge">
                    <i class="fas fa-clock"></i>
                    {{ medicalData.pharmacies|length }} établissements
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="table-container">
                <table>
                    <thead>
                        <tr>
                            <th>Pharmacie</th>
                            <th>Horaires</th>
                            <th>Contact</th>
                            <th>Adresse</th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                        {% for pharmacy in medicalData.pharmacies %}
                        <tr>
                            <td>
                                <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;">
                                    <i class="fas fa-flask" style="color: #0a4a2e; font-size: 20px;"></i>
                                    <strong>{{ pharmacy.name }}</strong>
                                </div>
                            </td>
                            <td>
                                <span class="badge badge-success">
                                    <i class="fas fa-calendar-check"></i>
                                    {{ pharmacy.hours }}
                                </span>
                            </td>
                            <td>
                                <span class="phone">
                                    <i class="fas fa-phone-alt"></i>
                                    {{ pharmacy.phone }}
                                </span>
                            </td>
                            <td>
                                <span class="address">
                                    <i class="fas fa-location-dot"></i>
                                    {{ pharmacy.address }}
                                </span>
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                        {% endfor %}
                    </tbody>
                </table>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Section Hôpitaux -->
        <div class="section">
            <div class="section-header">
                <div class="section-title">
                    <div class="section-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-hospital"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h2>Hôpitaux & Cliniques</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="section-badge">
                    <i class="fas fa-building"></i>
                    {{ medicalData.hospitals|length }} structures
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="table-container">
                <table>
                    <thead>
                        <tr>
                            <th>Établissement</th>
                            <th>Type</th>
                            <th>Contact</th>
                            <th>Adresse</th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                        {% for hospital in medicalData.hospitals %}
                        <tr>
                            <td>
                                <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;">
                                    <i class="fas fa-building" style="color: #0369a1; font-size: 20px;"></i>
                                    <strong>{{ hospital.name }}</strong>
                                </div>
                            </td>
                            <td>
                                <span class="badge badge-info">
                                    <i class="fas fa-tag"></i>
                                    {{ hospital.type }}
                                </span>
                            </td>
                            <td>
                                <span class="phone">
                                    <i class="fas fa-phone-alt"></i>
                                    {{ hospital.phone }}
                                </span>
                            </td>
                            <td>
                                <span class="address">
                                    <i class="fas fa-location-dot"></i>
                                    {{ hospital.address }}
                                </span>
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                        {% endfor %}
                    </tbody>
                </table>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Footer Premium -->
        <div class="footer">
            <div class="footer-info">
                <h3>
                    <i class="fas fa-heart" style="color: #ef4444;"></i>
                    StudyFlow Care
                </h3>
                <p>
                    Votre bien-être est notre mission. Ce répertoire regroupe des professionnels 
                    de santé engagés pour accompagner les étudiants dans leur parcours académique.
                </p>
                <div style="display: flex; gap: 20px; margin-top: 20px;">
                    <span style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;">
                        <i class="fas fa-check-circle" style="color: #10b981;"></i>
                        Professionnels certifiés
                    </span>
                    <span style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;">
                        <i class="fas fa-clock" style="color: #3b82f6;"></i>
                        Disponibles 7j/7
                    </span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="footer-stats">
                <div class="stat-item">
                    <div class="stat-value">{{ medicalData.psychiatrists|length + medicalData.pharmacies|length + medicalData.hospitals|length }}</div>
                    <div class="stat-label">Contacts</div>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-item">
                    <div class="stat-value">24/7</div>
                    <div class="stat-label">Urgences</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="confidential">
                <i class="fas fa-lock"></i>
                Document confidentiel - Destiné à un usage personnel StudyFlow
                <i class="fas fa-print" style="margin-left: 15px;"></i>
                <i class="fas fa-file-pdf" style="margin-left: 10px;"></i>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>